law.history: Repealed 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 445, sec. 14, effective July 14, 1992. -- Amended 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 445, effective January 2, 1978. -- Amended 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 126, sec. 41. -- Created 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 234, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Parole of persons confined in workhouse or penal farm of county containing city of first class.
